<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001879>
    dc:description "Figures 38. Tephritis vespertina. (A) Feeding damage caused by the third stage larva inside the flowerhead of Hypochoeris radicata L. (Asteraceae); (B) larva in situ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001881>
    dc:description "Figure 39. Acidia cognata, leaf mine in Tussilago farfara L. (Asteraceae), mine opened with larva in situ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001883>
    dc:description "Figure 40. Acidia cognata, leaf mine in Tussilago farfara L. Asteraceae: t = between the arrows, part of a feeding track; a = arcs within a feeding track." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001885>
    dc:description "Figures 41. Head skeletons of phytophagous species, lateral views, mandibles to the left. (A) Tephritis vespertina, length 0.3 mm; (B) Acidia cognata, length 0.6 mm; (C) Chaetostomella cylindrica, length 0.6 mm; (D) Botanophila seneciella, length 0.7 mm. Botanophila seneciella, drawing of mandible and intermediate sclerite: (E) lateral view with muscle tendons; (F) ventral view; (G) Pegomya solennis, length 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001888>
    dc:description "Figure 42. Pegomya solennis, preserved larva, thorax and pseudocephalon, head to the right, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001890>
    dc:description "Figures 43. Pegomya solennis, larva feeding in a leaf mine on Rumex acetosa (Polygonaceae), stills from Film 18. (A) Position at the start of a feeding lunge; (B) position at the end of a feeding lunge." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001899>
    dc:description "Figure 47. Pegomya solennis, preserved larva, lateral view, head to the right, length 8.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001899/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001901>
    dc:description "Figure 48. Acidia cognata, preserved larva, lateral view, head to the right, length 5.7 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4001901/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4001903>
    dc:description "Figure 49. Pegomya solennis, preserved larva, pseudocephalon, ventral view." ;
